race.comment: CITY OF LOVE (2) jumped cleanly last start and led all the way (21.95) at this track in a Novice race over 381m. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. ROAMIN' AROUND (1) doesn't win out of turn but looks close to breaking through. Has been in the money the last five starts, the latest when second (17.29) at Mandurah. Can feature again. PENNY PINCHER (8) had the drop on the lead before drawing clear to score (17.37) at Northam in a Novice race over 297m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. One of the leading chances again. EVANDER KEEPING (3) can return to form after missing the top-three at this circuit last time out.
